  <p class="date">Last updated: April 2026</p>
  <section><h2>1. Introduction</h2><p>Trouvé is a mobile application (Android and iOS) for searching PDF documents by keywords with AI-powered summaries. This policy explains how we collect, use and protect your data.</p></section>
  <section><h2>2. Data collected</h2><ul><li>PDF documents and images you voluntarily import</li><li>Text extracted from your documents for search</li><li>App preferences (language, dark mode)</li><li>Recently viewed documents</li></ul></section>
  <section><h2>3. Use of data</h2><ul><li>Extract text via Claude API (Anthropic)</li><li>Enable keyword search</li><li>Generate intelligent summaries</li><li>Remember your preferences</li></ul></section>
  <section><h2>4. Data sharing</h2><p>Your documents are sent to Anthropic's Claude API for text extraction. Anthropic processes this data according to their <a href="https://www.anthropic.com/privacy">privacy policy</a>. We do not sell your personal data.</p></section>
  <section><h2>5. Storage</h2><p>All your data is stored <strong>locally on your device</strong>. We do not use servers to store your personal documents.</p></section>
  <section><h2>6. Security</h2><ul><li>Data stored locally on your device</li><li>Encrypted communications via HTTPS</li><li>We have no access to your personal documents</li></ul></section>
  <section><h2>7. Your rights</h2><ul><li>Delete your documents from Settings</li><li>Uninstall the app to delete all data</li><li>Contact our support for any questions</li></ul></section>
  <section><h2>8. Children</h2><p>The app is not intended for children under 13 years old.</p></section>
  <section><h2>9. Changes</h2><p>We may update this policy at any time. Changes will be published on this page.</p></section>
  <div class="contact"><h2>10. Contact</h2><p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);margin-top:8px">For any questions:</p><p style="margin-top:12px"><a href="mailto:trouve.app@gmail.com">trouve.app@gmail.com</a></p></div>
